    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1649950/extras/96fed9b259e50943d23358527724873c.webp?t=1771927723\" width=616 height=59 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1649950/extras/c094390b6f58f809f0e6702d33c0f3ec.poster.avif?t=1771927723\" width=780 height=240 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1649950/extras/c094390b6f58f809f0e6702d33c0f3ec.webm?t=1771927723\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1649950/extras/c094390b6f58f809f0e6702d33c0f3ec.mp4?t=1771927723\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在《新闻大厦》中，投身1930年代纽约城的喧嚣与混乱，在这款模拟经营类游戏中打造并经营属于你的报纸。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >从大萧条到二战前夕，每个周日都是截稿日，每篇报道都关乎战略选择。在编辑困境、编辑室混乱与政治压力的夹缝中，你将亲手塑造报纸的未来，开创你的媒体帝国！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1649950/extras/c1005e064eedd4453ce1188d2ae78e01.webp?t=1771927723\" width=616 height=59 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1649950/extras/4d55c0a1c4f698e415df3cbe8b8de706.poster.avif?t=1771927723\" width=780 height=240 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1649950/extras/4d55c0a1c4f698e415df3cbe8b8de706.webm?t=1771927723\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1649950/extras/4d55c0a1c4f698e415df3cbe8b8de706.mp4?t=1771927723\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >从空白楼层开始，从零起步构建你的新闻编辑室。随着报社发展壮大，解锁新楼层，将每一层都打造成功能完备的新闻枢纽。从印刷站、排版台，到负责危机公关的法律部门，每个工作站都是保证报纸顺利付印的关键。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >明智的布局选择：墙体、电梯、气动管道将直接影响团队在压力下的工作效率。员工士气同样重要！添置咖啡机、海报和必不可少的室内绿植，提升员工的幸福指数！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >记者、摄影师、清洁工，还有不可或缺的广告销售员……领导一支由30多种独特职位组成的多元化团队，每位成员都拥有各自的特质、需求和专长。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >巧妙平衡饥饿度、专注力与后勤保障，以最大化生产效率。解锁从留声机到老虎机等数十种升级项目，将破旧塔楼改造为顶级工作空间。快乐的编辑室才是高效的编辑室，尤其是在截稿日步步紧逼之时！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1649950/extras/edb5b1df859b2fff436cc85b3b738b2b.webp?t=1771927723\" width=616 height=59 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1649950/extras/6c4b55e4d918108853d2e2665076fcd5.poster.avif?t=1771927723\" width=780 height=240 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1649950/extras/6c4b55e4d918108853d2e2665076fcd5.webm?t=1771927723\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1649950/extras/6c4b55e4d918108853d2e2665076fcd5.mp4?t=1771927723\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >记者、摄影师、清洁工，还有不可或缺的广告销售员……领导一支由30多种独特职位组成的多元化团队，每位成员都拥有各自的特质、需求和专长。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >巧妙平衡饥饿度、专注力与后勤保障，以最大化生产效率。解锁从留声机到老虎机等数十种升级项目，将破旧塔楼改造为顶级工作空间。快乐的编辑室才是高效的编辑室，尤其是在截稿日步步紧逼之时！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1649950/extras/26fd7b680b008b200989d7ed9be0ea6c.webp?t=1771927723\" width=616 height=59 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1649950/extras/3cbbb106652b25513b51ea835d5c6fe5.poster.avif?t=1771927723\" width=780 height=240 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1649950/extras/3cbbb106652b25513b51ea835d5c6fe5.webm?t=1771927723\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1649950/extras/3cbbb106652b25513b51ea835d5c6fe5.mp4?t=1771927723\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >每周的目标只有一个：赶在周日截稿前完成当期报纸。为记者分配采访选题方向，选择你的编辑方针，通过你选定的报道口吻和话题标签影响公众印象，最终完成报纸编排。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >聚焦犯罪、政治、体育等关键议题，调整报道角度以契合你的编辑方针。是深耕深度报道还是打造吸睛标题？你追求的是公信力还是传播力？</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >你的每个选择都会影响读者印象、舆论反应与报纸销量。拿捏得当则利润飙升，稍有差池则可能招致抵制、诉讼，甚至黑帮的“礼貌拜访”……</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1649950/extras/a584ed3b5ed16027183686b759e0d3b3.webp?t=1771927723\" width=616 height=59 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1649950/extras/6c17357ec0e307cc53cae931d220f2d5.poster.avif?t=1771927723\" width=780 height=240 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1649950/extras/6c17357ec0e307cc53cae931d220f2d5.webm?t=1771927723\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1649950/extras/6c17357ec0e307cc53cae931d220f2d5.mp4?t=1771927723\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >四大势力在这座城市里上演着权力割据：市长、黑手党、军方与上流社会。他们将推行自身议程，并以现金、影响力、独家奖励及遍布纽约城的重要人脉为筹码，提出暗箱交易。你将刊载谁的真相，又将掩埋谁的秘密？</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >并非所有人都拥护新闻自由……</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1649950/extras/2eb550c90e542fc49461cffd3b32f127.webp?t=1771927723\" width=616 height=59 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1649950/extras/8be4861094a72bd929295635023efec6.poster.avif?t=1771927723\" width=780 height=240 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1649950/extras/8be4861094a72bd929295635023efec6.webm?t=1771927723\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1649950/extras/8be4861094a72bd929295635023efec6.mp4?t=1771927723\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >将你的报纸发行至从哈莱姆到华尔街的纽约各区。每个行政区都有独特的读者画像、偏好和奖励机制。要扩大订阅群体，需根据本地口味定制报道，同时还要领先于两大强劲对手：《帝国观察报》与《泽西灯塔报》。他们会窃取你宝贵的独家新闻，但只要精准把握读者口味，你就能赢得他们的读者群，跻身成为纽约城最具影响力的出版商。</p>",
